name: KRED
public_notice: KRED (KRED) has migrated from their older BSC contract to a new one on Polygon. For more information, please view this announcement on Twitter.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
